      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a masterfully sorted performance machine for the discerning enthusiast. This specimen features a blueprinted power plant with forged rotating assembly components and a precision-balanced crankshaft for vibration-free high-RPM operation. The induction system utilizes a bespoke high-flow intake manifold and a remapped ECU for optimized air-fuel ratios and aggressive timing curves. Suspension kinematics have been refined with adjustable coilovers and reinforced bushings to eliminate deflection under heavy cornering loads. Thermal efficiency is maximized via a multi-core aluminum radiator and a dedicated transmission cooler. The drivetrain is anchored by a short-throw shifter and a stage 2 clutch with high-friction organic lining for instantaneous engagement. Zero deferred maintenance\u2014this is a turnkey platform optimized for peak mechanical output and chassis rigidity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
